OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1776787870
OL,3,CResidents told to leave their homes
OL,4,Cafter huge blaze breaks out in
OL,5,CHuddersfield
OL,7,FScores of resident have been told to
OL,8,Fleave their homes and one of
OL,9,FHuddersfield busiest roads was closed
OL,10,Fto traffic as 17 fire crews tackled a
OL,11,Fhuge blaze at an industrial unit.
OL,13,FDiversions were put in place after the
OL,14,Ffire broke out around lunchtime.
OL,16,FWest Yorkshire Fire and rescue
OL,17,Fdeployed 15 fire engines and two
OL,18,Faerial appliances to fight the fire
OL,19,Foff Leeds Road, which was closed in
OL,20,Fboth directions from Stocks Bank Road
OL,21,Fto Far Common Road.
